translations.2728816764897880742: Founded in 2015 our community qbitmc has focused on bringing a vanilla experiences to its members with a technical & aesthetic turn. Inspired on the hermitcraft server each and one of us have our own base and get involved into trust-based trading on the shopping district of the server. We also come together every now and then to collaborate on big community projects such as automated farms and buildings
